# Section 13 — Production Readiness Assessment

---

# 13.1 Introduction

Successfully deploying an AI application is only one milestone in the software lifecycle.

Enterprise systems require significantly more than functional correctness.

A production-ready AI platform must address:

- Reliability
- Scalability
- Security
- Observability
- Maintainability
- Recoverability
- Governance

This chapter evaluates the Study Abroad Finder against those characteristics.

The objective is not to criticize the current implementation, but to identify the gap between a working Proof of Concept (PoC) and an enterprise-grade production system.

