# 13.4 Security Assessment

## Current State

Secrets are managed using

```
Environment Variables
```

Examples

```
GOOGLE_API_KEY

GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY

TAVILY_API_KEY
```

This is significantly better than embedding secrets inside source code.

---

## Recommended Improvements

Enterprise deployments should use

- Google Secret Manager

or

- AWS Secrets Manager

or

- Azure Key Vault

instead of

```
.env
```

files.

